Where is God in the storm ?
But when your goin thru a “secret storm” it’s no comfort or noone there because noone knows that your dealing with anything...

For the past 2 months I personally have been going thru a “Secret Storm”,  See when your going thru a visible storm somebody will hand you some assistance like a poncho, maye an umbrella, because they are aware of your suffering...

Has anyone ever been in a “Storm”? 
I’m talking about the storms that make people think you haven’t been through anything. Because you put your hair & make up on, & people don’t know you put your smile on just like you did you make up
Sometimes when you enter into a “Storm”, and there are all kinds of storms, Health storms, physical storms, financial storms, emotional storms, It’s all kinds of storms,
Don’t take the presence of the storm to indicate the absence of God.
